believe it's folklore.

41:11.136 --> 41:12.803
Maybe they want to make it real.

41:12.971 --> 41:15.097
Yeah, like I just said,
James Capisi...

41:15.306 --> 41:17.141
There's no woman in white,
Miss Preaker.

41:17.225 --> 41:20.102
Trust me, it's a man did this.

